  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Custom Trigger</h2>
    <p>Provide your own trigger button as a child element with <code>data-trigger</code>. If no trigger is found, one is auto-created.</p>

    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Custom trigger button">{{ customTriggerCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Without Target</h2>
    <p>Omit the <code>for</code> attribute to use the picker without auto-insertion. Listen for the <code>emoji-select</code> event and handle insertion yourself.</p>

    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Event-only mode">{{ noTargetCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

